{"title":"红柳是个村子","authors":["董雯"],"dates":[{"year":1994,"month":9,"day":23}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"红柳是个村子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"董雯"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红柳是个村名"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就在山的半腰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从古传下来的红柳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"年年岁岁在黄沙地里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唱着祖先唱过的歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一条褪色的补丁裤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"已经走过好几个年头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日子在母亲补裤子时"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"默默耗尽最后一点灯油"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天昨天还有前天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有什么区别"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄沙在风里就那么一天天转"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"第一个走出红柳的娃"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叫石头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"补丁的裤一步步在山口隐没"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山外的日头亮得晃眼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"石头的眼里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红柳就恍成一片黄沙的云"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朴素得让人心酸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"母亲的泪滴下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把黄沙打成一个小坑窝"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昏浊的泪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"落在掌心"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"粗糙的掌上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就捧了一颗期待的心"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天长日久"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那山口处的母亲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"站成一座山崖"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"面向山外"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"望烟雨流火"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"望雁去雁来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"终于望穿封尘的岁月"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"望见了黄沙幻化的诗意……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}